      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 high-revving inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example has undergone a comprehensive mechanical vetting, including a documented VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and rear subframe reinforcement\u2014the 'Big Three' for this chassis. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, paired with a perfectly functioning M-variable differential lock for optimal power delivery. The suspension maintains its factory-spec handling characteristics with refreshed bushings and OEM Sachs dampers. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior demonstrates zero bolster wear or pixel degradation. A turn-key specimen for the serious enthusiast.",
