      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly pristine 2021 BMW M2 Competition in Hockenheim Silver Metallic. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. The 19-inch forged wheels are free of any curb rash and are wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. Inside, the Black Dakota leather with contrast blue stitching remains supple and shows no signs of wear, even on the driver-side bolsters; it retains that factory-new scent and has never been smoked in. Every electronic feature and driver assist works perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a full service history documented exclusively through BMW authorized centers. This is a single-owner, accident-free vehicle that has never seen a track day or inclement weather. It includes both original keys, all manuals, and the original window sticker. For the buyer seeking a 'new' car experience from a pre-owned enthusiast vehicle, this is the benchmark.",
